1993&ndash;2010&rdquo;, NCJ239203, Special Report, U.S. Department of
Justice, Office of Justice Programs, Bureau of Justice Statistics,
November 2012.
 [<a href="https://bjs.ojp.gov/content/pub/pdf/ipv9310.pdf" target="other">Catalano 2012 available online</a>]</li>
 
